title: No player iconq
body: It has been like 5 days and i have still not received the star guardian icon but my friend got it immediately what can i do to fix this

replies.body: It can take a few days for the icon to unlock on the account, and some players may receive it before others.  As long as you were logged in to the site with the intended account while taking the quiz, you'll be fine.  The goods will come!
